column5: Anyone fishing the "Fort" tourny this coming weekend? Its the second last one on the "sask walleye trail" Fishing there hasnt been the best... very very windy... came up with a 16 pound weight today though... well if any of u are fishing it hope to hear from u... Im 19 and my partner is 17.. This will be or fourth tourny this year... I guess there arent very many young teams around..... later
